{"id": 2456, "genre": 1004, "title": "【好奇心X新福特翼虎】测一测你是哪一种车型人格？", "description": "讲真的，开不同车子的人代表不同性格。", "record_count": 11728, "comment_count": 53, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180709104759qNzfwGHvKod2aPnl.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-09T03:21:05Z", "column": null, "normal_questions": [{"id": 4484, "content": "在你的日常生活中，「汽车」在你心里是怎样的角色？", "image": "img/question/question/20180709104839rZGq4vC17U5XAPQn.jpg", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 291728, "title": "日常的代步工具而已", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291729, "title": " 自己的私密空间", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291730, "title": "带一点小炫耀的存在", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291731, "title": "自由的象征，可以说走就走", "score": 3.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4485, "content": "闲暇时间，你最常选择怎样的方式度过？", "image": "img/question/question/20180709105040JUoLyGTxRwbEqu43.jpg", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 291732, "title": "开车出去郊区兜兜风", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291733, "title": "宅在家里陪家人 ", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291734, "title": "和朋友在市中心聚会", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291735, "title": "看喜欢的剧团演出", "score": 2.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4486, "content": "出门旅行，你更喜欢哪种方式?", "image": "img/question/question/201807091051429rBg3Z5jGliKAVqQ.jpg", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 291736, "title": "去环境、设施好的高级度假区", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291737, "title": "巴黎、米兰等时尚圣地打卡", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291738, "title": "川藏线、美国1号公路等自驾", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291739, "title": "家庭游，比如陪父母爬山", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4487, "content": "以下场景，哪个让你觉得有安全感", "image": "img/question/question/20180709105254z3OmeZbSTuiyP40H.png", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 291740, "title": "一个密闭的小空间，有音乐有你熟悉的摆件", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291741, "title": "在家里的客厅里，沙发上", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291742, "title": "和相爱的人呆着，哪里都是安全感十足", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291743, "title": "有存在感，才有安全感", "score": 1.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4488, "content": "当你走在路上，被迎面而来的人给撞了一下，你会？", "image": "img/question/question/201807091053514ZThc6utV8mgaXRl.png", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 291744, "title": "笑笑，不当回事", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291745, "title": "拉住他，让他道歉", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291746, "title": "心里默默的骂一句脏话", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291747, "title": "赶紧整理一下被蹭的衣装", "score": 1.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4489, "content": "出门在外，你经常什么样的着装？", "image": "img/question/question/20180709105443Szq9m7fdL8tOoglG.png", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 291748, "title": "尽量正式一些", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291749, "title": "百变风格百变造型", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291750, "title": "随意点，自己舒服就行", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291751, "title": "必须是潮流大牌", "score": 1.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4490, "content": " 繁忙的工作结束，突然来了朋友夜晚的邀约，你会？", "image": "img/question/question/20180709105615bzvqXFRWHQlB20Vo.png", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 291752, "title": "直接拒绝，想回家休息", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291753, "title": "还是去吧，毕竟朋友要紧", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291754, "title": "找找理由，比如下班堵车不方便？", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291755, "title": "爽快答应，并把自己装扮一番", "score": 1.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4491, "content": "以下哪种行为你绝对不能接受？", "image": "img/question/question/20180709105718Ywhsgf4k20Ob8Fax.png", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 291756, "title": "向你借车出去玩", "score": 3.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291757, "title": "想和你拼车出门", "score": 1.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291758, "title": "在你车上吃东西", "score": 2.0, "image": null}, {"id": 291759, "title": "和你一起兜风，但着装很土", "score": 1.0, "image": null}]}]}